The Champagne 2020 vintage is the third high quality and very warm harvest in a row; a trilogy of vintages that resembles 1988, &rsquo;89 and 90, in terms of quality, but picked much earlier.&nbsp;
Gloriously ripe but balanced and practically disease free, 2020&rsquo;s potential was recognised at the time of the harvest. 
